@Node ConfigFiles "ConfigFiles"

  Config Files
  ============

    Progdir:Wall.CFG - Automatically generated
    ------------------------------------------

      MaxItems - maximum items to ever be displayed regardless of users
                 screen setting

      WallItems - must range from _1 to _<MaxItems> or less.
                  list of lines of text

@EndNode

